&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/WICKET-6006&quot; title=&quot;ModalWindow.closeCurrent() causes 414 status error&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;WICKET-6006&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;WICKET-6006&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; ModalWindow.closeCurrent() causes 414 status error&lt;/p&gt;

